Comment: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul?
