Comment: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Oh, there're mysteries and miseries
Comment: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Dead or alive　狭間に揺られて
Comment: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}彷徨えば　Right to left to hell
Comment: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}孤独の招待　感情の消退
Comment: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Comment: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
Comment: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}仮面の淵へ　手を掛けどただ骨が鳴るのみ
Comment: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Wars and swords, tears and blood
Comment: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:08.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}溢る力が　不意に嗤い出した
Comment: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:14.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Comment: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Comment: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Comment: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}理解らない　構わない
Comment: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}紛い力振るっても
Comment: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:34.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜けよ
Comment: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:39.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}嗚呼　失くした哀しみがまた疼いてく…
Comment: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Misery-World
